<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Die When You Die 2026</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            background: #080808;
            color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body,
        html {
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: #060606;
        }

        #splash {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #080808;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        #skull {
            position: relative;
            width: 220px;
            height: 260px;
            animation: shake 1.2s ease-in-out forwards;
        }

        #skull::before,
        #skull::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: #f5f3f0;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        #skull::before {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            top: 0;
            left: 20px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 120px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 120px;
        }

        #skull::after {
            width: 120px;
            height: 130px;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border-radius: 0 0 60px 60px;
        }

        .eye {
            position: absolute;
            width: 44px;
            height: 58px;
            background: #080808;
            border-radius: 50% 50% 40% 40%;
            top: 70px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px #f5f3f0 inset;
        }

        .eye.left {
            left: 44px;
            transform: rotate(-10deg);
        }

        .eye.right {
            right: 44px;
            transform: rotate(10deg);
        }

        .nose {
            position: absolute;
            top: 138px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(45deg);
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            background: #080808;
            border-radius: 0 50% 50% 50%;
        }

        .teeth {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 16px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .tooth {
            width: 18px;
            height: 28px;
            background: #080808;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .crack {
            position: absolute;
            width: 6px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #f5f3f0;
            top: 20px;
            left: 108px;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #080808;
            animation: crackMove 0.8s ease-in-out forwards;
        }

        .crack::before,
        .crack::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: #f5f3f0;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .crack::before {
            top: 18px;
            left: -8px;
        }

        .crack::after {
            top: 46px;
            left: 2px;
        }

        @keyframes crackMove {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(0) rotate(15deg);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            70% {
                transform: translateX(22px) translateY(-18px) rotate(35deg);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateX(44px) translateY(-38px) rotate(55deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }

            20% {
                transform: scale(1.02) rotate(-6deg);
            }

            40% {
                transform: scale(0.98) rotate(6deg);
            }

            60% {
                transform: scale(1.04) rotate(-4deg);
            }

            80% {
                transform: scale(0.98) rotate(4deg);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        .hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: opacity .4s ease, visibility .4s ease;
        }

        #content {
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: opacity .8s ease 0.2s, visibility 0s linear .8s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100%;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        #content.show {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transition-delay: 0s;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 5rem);
            margin-bottom: .6rem;
            letter-spacing: .08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        p {
            max-width: 650px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #d6d3d0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="splash">
        <div id="skull">
            <div class="eye left"></div>
            <div class="eye right"></div>
            <div class="nose"></div>
            <div class="teeth">
                <div class="tooth"></div>
                <div class="tooth"></div>
                <div class="tooth"></div>
                <div class="tooth"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="crack"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="content">

        <p>Why is existence so painful?</p>
        <p>Couldn't I just be put away and stored. Forgotten and Silent</p>
        <p>Like a pack of Ramen noodles that fell behind the fridge.</p>
        <h1>DieWhenYouDie 2026</h1>
        <p>Every day we go on, thinking and feeling and hurting.</p>
        <p>Looking forward to the great escape. The glorious release</p>
        <p>Death will embrace us with a sigh of relief</p>
    </div>
    <script>
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            setTimeout(function() {
                document.getElementById('splash').classList.add('hidden');
                document.getElementById('content').classList.add('show');
            }, 2600);
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>